      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-rig-umi-000      thru acc-rig-umi-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-rig    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-cor-reg-900.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-cor-reg-300.
       acc-cor-reg-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
